## REFERENCIAS

Malik, N., Mohideen, E. R., Ali, L., Faheem, M., y otros autores. Chameleon Swarm Algorithm: A Bio-Inspired Optimizer for Solving Engineering Design Problems.


NetLogo 3D. Plataforma de modelado basada en agentes desarrollada por Uri Wilensky, Center for Connected Learning and Computer-Based Modeling, Northwestern University.

